====Translations====
*Dutch: [[af]], [[uit]]
*Vietnamese: [[đi]], [[ra#Vietnamese|ra]] (see individual verb for which translation to use)

===Adjective===
'''off'''

# Not [[operating]], [[disabled]].
#:''All the lights are '''off'''.''
# [[rotten]]
#:''This milk is '''off'''!''
# {{cricket}} In, or towards the [[half]] of the [[field]] away from the [[batsman]]'s [[leg]]s; the [[right]] side for a [[right-handed]] batsman.

====Antonyms====
*(1): [[on]]
*(2): [[fresh]]
*(3): [[on]], [[leg]]

