===Preposition===
'''off'''

<!-- Most uses thought of as prepositions are actually adverbial. True prepositional uses are mostly idiomatic. -->
# (''informal'') [[from]]
#:''I got it '''off''' the internet.''
#:''This song is '''off''' their second album.''

====Antonyms====
*[[on]]

